[[File:Cosmic talisman detail.png|left|120px]]
A '''cosmic talisman''' is a [[talisman]] needed to enter the [[Cosmic Altar]] in the southern part of [[Zanaris]]. It can be combined with a [[tiara]] to make a [[cosmic tiara]] for 40 [[Runecraft]] [[experience]] at the Cosmic Altar by using the tiara on the altar. This makes the talisman disappear, but the tiara can be used in just the same way and can be worn. Both the tiara and the talisman allow players to craft [[cosmic rune]]s at level 27 Runecraft.

To enter the altar the player needs to have completed the [[Lost City]] quest or [[Enter the Abyss]] if using the Abyss.

Cosmic talismans can be obtained from monsters and also a possible reward from [[random events]], as well as [[casket]]s obtained via [[big fishing net]]s or killing [[Rock Crabs]], [[Sand Crab]]s and [[Ammonite Crab]]s.
